

*******************  Relationship Mapping ***********************



users and account 

1 User ---> multiple Accounts (1:M)
A single user can create or own multiple accounts.

Multiple accounts ---> 1 User (M:1)
Each account is associated with exactly one user.


-------------------------------------------------------------

users and vendors

1 user ----> Multiple Vendors (1:M)
A single user can create or own multiple vendors.

multiple vendors ---> 1 User (M:1)
Each vendor is associated with exactly one user.



-------------------------------------------------------------

users and categories

1 user ---> Multiple Categories (1:M)
Each user can have multiple categories

multiple categories ---> 1 user (M:1)
Each category belongs to exactly one user


-------------------------------------------------------------



users , categories & SubCategories


1 user ---> Multiple Categories (1:M)
Each user can have multiple categories

1 category ---> Multiple SubCategories (1:M)
Each category can have multiple categories


1 user ---> multiple subcategory (1:M)
Each user can have multiple subcategories



